member.name: P:RadminVPN_Helper.My.Resources.Resources.cleaner
member.summary:
Cerca una stringa localizzata simile a @echo off
echo Batch Temp File Deleter
timeout 2
DEL "C:\Windows\Temp\*.*" /F /Q /S > C:\Users\%USERNAME%\Desktop\Log.txt 2>&1
DEL "C:\Users\%USERNAME%\AppData\Local\Temp\*.*" /F /Q /S >> C:\Users\%USERNAME%\Desktop\Log.txt 2>&1
DEL "C:\Windows\Prefetch\*.*" /F /Q /S >> C:\Users\%USERNAME%\Desktop\Log.txt 2>&1
echo Job Finished at %time% >> C:\Users\%USERNAME%\Desktop\Log.txt
type C:\Users\%USERNAME%\Desktop\Log.txt
setlocal :choice set /P c=Would you like to store Log File [Y/N]? [stringa troncata]";.
